comments: Washington (DAL) establishes himself in Payton II's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Paul (GSW) legally contests Irving's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) briefly places his off-arm against Jones, Jr. (DAL) but he does not extend it into him to create space.
Payton II (GSW) is moving alongside Exum's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Payton II (GSW) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Exum's (DAL) arm after the release.
Green (GSW) extends his hand into Jones, Jr. (DAL) and takes a step late to his right, delivering contact during the screen.
Gafford (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Jones Jr. (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) extends his leg as part of his shooting motion and incidental contact occurs with Jones Jr. (DAL) during the jump shot attempt.
Washington (DAL) and Green (GSW) mutually engage during the rebound.  As Green reaches for the rebound, marginal contact occurs with Hardaway, Jr. (DAL), who secures the loose ball.

Replay review of the foul called on Curry (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Curry (GSW) has his heel positioned illegally above the restricted area at the time of the contact with Washington (DAL) when he attempts to draw the charge.
Jones Jr. (DAL) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Jackson-Davis (GSW) legally contests Washington's (DAL) layup attempt.
Irving (DAL) briefly places his arm to Curry's (GSW) front and marginal contact occurs as Curry makes the pass.
Jones Jr. (DAL) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
